<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 xiǎo yáng hū shēng yī piàn, nǐ xīn zài hé fāng?
 zhǔ jīn rì yào yòng nǐ, shì fǒu néng xiàn shàng?
 zhuāng jià dào chù fā bái, néng fǒu shàng hé chǎng?
 yǒu rén xū yào bāng zhù, néng fǒu xiàn lì liàng?
 xiàn zài xiàn zài dāng yīn qín, zhèng shì hǎo shí guāng,
 zhǔ gěi nǐ de ēn diǎn, qiān wàn mò yǐn cáng.</lyrics>
<title>xiǎo yáng hū shēng yī piàn 迦南163</title>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>163</hymn_number>
</song>